Today on the show we had the leaders of the Whore Hive, Mandi and Weezy from the Whoreible Decisions Podcast and they spoke on everything sexual which works perfect fro Freaky Friday! Also, Angela nominated the first woman of color elected to Congress Patsy Mink for mandating equal treatment for women.
